{"tid":1014590,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"動畫《領風者》開播大受好評  網友表示追到底","createTime":"2019-02-09T10:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T04:43:14.000Z","uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6a1e27cdb48307e82db97e92c717f8a24a4ef308","tid":1014590,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T10:27:25.000Z","msg":"近日一部講述&ldquo;千年思想家&rdquo;卡爾&middot;馬克思一生的傳奇故事的動畫《領風者》在B站開播，收到了意想不到的點播量和好評。《領風者》動畫第一集開播3天就有超300W的播放量，大家對本作的評價也是相當不錯。《領風者》動畫在製作上有著不錯的水準，兩首主題歌曲各有風格，都相當好聽。網友們紛紛表示非常喜歡這種題材的動畫，要一直追下去。<br />\n<br />\n點擊觀看動畫《領風者》第一集：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/bangumi/play/ss26190?spm_id_from=333.334.b_72616e6b696e675f74696d696e675f67756f636875616e67.1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fbangumi%2Fplay%2Fss26190%3Fspm_id_from%3D333.334.b_72616e6b696e675f74696d696e675f67756f636875616e67.1&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=af788a71\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/bangumi/play/ss26190?spm_id_from=333.334.b_72616e6b696e675f74696d696e675f67756f636875616e67.1</a><br />\n<br />\n　　《領風者》講述了&ldquo;千年思想家&rdquo;卡爾&middot;馬克思一生的傳奇故事。馬克思既是頂天立地的偉人，他窮其一生構建的思想體系，喚醒了全世界沉睡中的無產階級，深刻影響了世界歷史發展的格局。馬克思也是有血有肉的常人，他與燕妮被阻撓的愛情、與恩格斯差點錯過的友誼，最後都成為了傳世佳話。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FAdcEYk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFAdcEYk.jpg&h=455f60db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNCkORF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNCkORF.jpg&h=de4efe39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ThaOdim.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FThaOdim.jpg&h=aa8c12bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aKzWnbG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaKzWnbG.jpg&h=1f3303a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/76HH2bH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F76HH2bH.jpg&h=82367385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tVCT8RH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtVCT8RH.jpg&h=5d70d9e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59280a92120971e90930c48af407275f13089e67","tid":1014590,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T10:29:59.000Z","msg":"bl?"},{"pid":"43df9b2e52407d4dd22380f16ca9d72df3fb2490","tid":1014590,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T10:30:09.000Z","msg":"【習權時代】南京大學生禁研究馬克思 要求解釋卻遭暴力驅散<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181103/58870841\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181103%2F58870841&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=9238d8c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181103%2F58870841&h=f32a90d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181103/58870841</a><br />\n<br />\n睇好喇,唔好去研究D乜野乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7054fad2bc23666d812285a45cf45fb6a31a2b3d","tid":1014590,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T10:33:23.000Z","msg":"點解唔出澤東傳?"},{"pid":"046b7db61e4283be2749bbcac02c49dc6c111ea5","tid":1014590,"uid":53524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T11:13:18.000Z","msg":"馬克思居然成為二次元人物!為紀念共產主義思想家馬克思誕辰200周年，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支國原創動畫</span>《領風者》將於28日在影視網站「嗶哩嗶哩」首播。<br />\n<br />\n放大十倍<div style=\"text-align: left;\"></div><br />\n食屎啦po埋d仆街膳稿"},{"pid":"cd5e859fd7b9834598ebc1f434b7452181758e1a","tid":1014590,"uid":91753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"046b7db61e4283be2749bbcac02c49dc6c111ea5","tid":1014590,"uid":53524,"like":2,"dislike":0,